      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I'd recommend Option C, Sterling Heights. The combination of modern architecture, high-end boutiques, and international dining options screams luxury and sophistication, evoking the image of a cosmopolitan playground for the elite. The fact that it's a waterfront enclave adds to its prestige, implying exclusivity and access to the finer things in life. It's the perfect setting for a high-end brochure targeting those seeking prestige and cultural refinement.",
