      "content": "I see. Why do you think Sterling Heights is a better fit for \"cultural refinement\" than Oak Ridge? Oak Ridge mentions classical music halls and historic libraries, which usually implies a very deep and sophisticated cultural history. Wouldn't that be considered more \"refined\" than the modern, fast-paced vibe of Sterling Heights?",
