      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's an interesting perspective. What about the Meridian District? You didn't mention it at all, but it was described as having a \"rich community\" and a \"vibrant culinary scene.\" Someone might argue that a deep, diverse cultural connection is actually more \"refined\" and \"cultured\" than just shopping at high-end boutiques. Why would a high-net-worth client avoid a place like that in favor of Sterling Heights?",
